(32116, 'levoleucovorin', 'N/A', 'minor', '7 DRUG INTERACTIONS Folic acid in large amounts may counteract the antiepileptic effect of phenobarbital, phenytoin and primidone, and increase the frequency of seizures in susceptible children.', 'DailyMed'),
